text: Ameesha Patel (; born Amisha Amit Patel on June 9, 1975) is an Indian actress, producer, and model who mainly appears in Bollywood films. She has also appeared in a few Telugu films and one Tamil film. She is notable for lots of films, including and especially her debut film Kaho Naa... Pyaar Hai. She has won a Filmfare Award for films like her debut film Kaho Naa...
